00:12:11,690 --> 00:12:13,030
into a larger context.

238
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:15,370
So typically,
you're going to have

239
00:12:15,370 --> 00:12:18,760
to go through a
series of steps here

240
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:22,930
