524
00:26:46,037 --> 00:26:48,370
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN: Beth
somehow got the really two hard

525
00:26:48,370 --> 00:26:48,870
readings.

526
00:26:48,870 --> 00:26:51,270
I don't know how she
lost in the jump ball.

527
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:57,520
But lily will take the
next couple of readings,

528
00:26:57,520 --> 00:27:01,390
