society and economy.

1301
01:04:29,620 --> 01:04:32,430
So there is a fast
growth period here--

1302
01:04:32,430 --> 01:04:35,177
maybe that's a decade.

1303
01:04:35,177 --> 01:04:36,760
Then there's a period
of more stable--

1304
01:04:36,760 --> 01:04:39,990
there's always a
bubble and then there's

1305
01:04:39,990 --> 01:04:42,930
