1306
01:04:42,930 --> 01:04:45,420
And maybe that's 20
years, maybe that's more.

1307
01:04:45,420 --> 01:04:50,070
And then eventually, you reach
kind of technological maturity.

1308
01:04:50,070 --> 01:04:55,050
So the IT wave, the one you all
are most familiar with that's

1309
01:04:55,050 --> 01:04:58,680
