1310
01:04:58,680 --> 01:05:00,160
When do we start it from?

1311
01:05:00,160 --> 01:05:03,330
Do we start it from
Babbage, do we start it

1312
01:05:03,330 --> 01:05:04,890
from Vannevar
Bush's differential

1313
01:05:04,890 --> 01:05:09,210
analyzer in the 1930s, do
we start it from ENIAC--

1314
01:05:09,210 --> 01:05:14,790
1946, the first functioning
mainframe computer.

1315
01:05:14,790 --> 01:05:16,290
We can start it
at various points,

1316
01:05:16,290 --> 01:05:18,660
but you get a sense for
